				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10497008/scp-4881#post-4173641</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2019 07:47:52 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Short and sweet, and I'm glad to see the word &quot;catkin&quot; on the site, since I remember first learning it while reading a literary magazine with a legend of a little cat named catkin, who answered fairy poem riddles where a willow was the answer for one (<em>&quot;So be it, though I am not high, my magic branches sweep the sky.&quot;</em>).</p> <p>+1 for the sweetness, and the memories.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
